+# Preview Generator V2 Control Class Boundaries - PR_26126_041
+
+Goal:
+- Enforce one control/section per class while preserving Preview Generator V2 behavior.
+
+Runtime behavior:
+- Preserved. No generation logic was rewritten.
+- PreviewGeneratorV2App remains the coordinator for the generation flow and delegates UI state/event ownership to controls.
+
+Boundary changes:
+- Renamed MenuSampleControl to GeneratePreviewControl.
+- Renamed StatusControl to StatusLogControl.
+- Moved direct UI DOM lookups out of PreviewGeneratorV2App and into PreviewGeneratorV2Ui/control classes.
+- PreviewGeneratorV2Ui now constructs the section controls with documentRef and exposes the same coordinator-facing control surface.
